      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but 4,000 seems so low if i'm actually deficient? i was reading on this wellness forum that if you do a \"loading dose\" of 50k for like 10 days it actually fixes the deficiency way faster than taking tiny amounts every day. i don't really have time for doctor appointments right now, i just want to know if doing it for a strictly limited time is actually dangerous or if it's just being overly cautious. like, is there any real risk if i only do it for a week or two?",
